sif3.common.model
Class PagingInfo

java.lang.Object
  sif3.common.model.PagingInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class PagingInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

When retrieveing large data sets from providers it is deemed unacceptable to return all data every time. This class is used to provide 'paging' style information to providers.

Author:
Joerg Huber
